  "description": "## Deep Component Audit ‚Äî hx-slider\n\n**Component directory:** `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-slider/`\n**wc-mcp Health Score:** 90 (A)\n**Known issues:** formAssociated, _internals, _hasLabelSlot, _hasMinLabelSlot, _hasMaxLabelSlot, _hasHelpSlot, _input, _sliderId, _labelId, _helpId ‚Äî all missing descriptions.\n\n### wc-mcp Tools ‚Äî USE THESE\n- `score_component`, `get_component`, `analyze_accessibility`, `validate_usage`, `list_css_parts`, `list_events`, `get_design_tokens`\n- **Report wc-mcp bugs to `/Volumes/Development/booked/wc-tools` board.**\n\n### Audit Scope\n1. **Design Tokens** ‚Äî `--hx-` tokens. Track, fill, thumb, labels. Dark mode.\n2. **Accessibility** ‚Äî WCAG 2.1 AA. slider role. aria-valuenow/min/max/valuetext. Keyboard (arrow keys). Label association.\n3. **Functionality** ‚Äî Min/max/step. Value. Labels (min/max/current). Form integration. Validation. Marks/ticks.\n4. **TypeScript** ‚Äî Strict. formAssociated. No `any`.\n5. **CSS/Styling** ‚Äî Shadow DOM. CSS Parts (track, fill, thumb). Cross-browser thumb styling.\n6. **CEM Accuracy** ‚Äî Fix all 10 missing descriptions.\n7. **Tests** ‚Äî 80%+ coverage. Value changes. Keyboard. Form. ARIA. Step.\n8. **Storybook** ‚Äî Basic. With labels. Step. Min/max. Disabled.\n9. **Drupal Compatibility** ‚Äî Range input. Twig-friendly.\n10. **Portability** ‚Äî CDN-ready. Form-associated.\n\n### Deliverable\nDetailed audit report. Fix CRITICAL+HIGH. Document rest.",
